{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hi! I'm Alexander and this is my game KoChaos! This is a project I've been working on since 2020. Me and a buddy always discussed wanting to make a game in middle school and I went for it. It took me forever to get the idea down but I think I've got it. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In KoChaos, you aim to defeat minions and bosses to collect XP to get extremely powerful. There are four difficulties that you can use to your advantage. Start small on Easy and work your way to Ko difficulty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are eight heroes you can level up to your heart's content. Each has three abilities and there primary attacks to use at your disposal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are tons of bosses to fight and conquer as well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Features-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- You can use glowing emerald swords. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Every bit of XP you gain for a hero stays with that hero and the stats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- The longer you play the easier the game becomes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Guns are here for some reason. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Dash like never before!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- You can infinitely ascend your heroes to make them extremely powerful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- No cap on stats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- The enemies have one eye.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I hope you hop in the game and enjoy!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727550/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737770561","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727550/page.bg.jpg?t=1737770561","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727550/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737770561","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727550/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737770561","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hi! I'm Alexander and this is my game KoChaos! This is a project I've been working on since 2020. Me and a buddy always discussed wanting to make a game in middle school and I went for it. It took me forever to get the idea down but I think I've got it. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In KoChaos, you aim to defeat minions and bosses to collect XP to get extremely powerful. There are four difficulties that you can use to your advantage. Start small on Easy and work your way to Ko difficulty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are eight heroes you can level up to your heart's content. Each has three abilities and there primary attacks to use at your disposal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are tons of bosses to fight and conquer as well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Features-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- You can use glowing emerald swords. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Every bit of XP you gain for a hero stays with that hero and the stats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- The longer you play the easier the game becomes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Guns are here for some reason. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Dash like never before!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- You can infinitely ascend your heroes to make them extremely powerful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- No cap on stats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- The enemies have one eye.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I hope you hop in the game and enjoy!</p>","developers":["Alexander Herbert","Luca Young"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Casual"